Articles.Content:
I had a very weird bug that happened to me in KSP recently, I do not know what is the cause of it, I only edited the game data files for some mods and add-ons, and I entirely do not know what to do to stop this.

Ingame, I cannot deploy solar panels for some reason , whenever i right click solar panels , i don't see the deploy button.

list of mods:

CameraTools

Chatterer

EVE

SVE

SVT

Kopernicus

MechJeb2

PlanetShine

Realplume

scatterer

TextureReplacer

VanguardTechnologies

KIS

KAS

HullCameraVDS
